flowchart TD
    A[Anonymous visitor or first operator] --> B[setup_wizard entry]
    B --> C[SetupWizardController]
    C --> D{Host setup wizard completed?}
    D -- no --> E[Redirect to platform_details step]
    E --> F[Render host platform form]
    F --> G[SetupWizardStepsController#create_host_platform]
    G --> H[find_or_initialize_by host:true]
    H --> I[Update existing host platform or create first one]
    I --> J[Mark step complete]
    J --> K[Proceed to admin creation]
    D -- yes --> L{Signed in?}
    L -- yes --> M[Redirect to root with already completed alert]
    L -- no --> N[Redirect to sign in with already completed alert]
